	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=122872><span id=Sage>lugernet</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>25 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Hello Friends,<br>Non-Necro here, seeking advice; I’ve been playing a Rogue for the last 3 months straight, nothing else. &amp; I must say, though I love him – I need something new. I’ve always been intrigued with Necro’s &amp; now I’m looking to start one. I’ve scanned a few pages of posts, it seems we have some gurus and sages lurking the boards!! Already I’ve seen some helpful information, but I’m still looking for more.<br><br>[The Obvious]<br>1= What’s the best Race (…asked in an earlier post, but left out Gnomes)?<br>2= What should I put my initial points into?<br>3= What weapon skill do I need? (1HP, 1HS, 1HB, etc.)?<br>4= What’s the Necro epic?<br>5= I’d also appreciate any links; I can find the obvious class specific links through Allakhazam’s, but there’s more I’m guessing…<br><br>Most of this information I could eventually find through the major EQ info-sites. But like most of you probably know, Forum’s are the best for advice based off experience. I would appreciate any advice you Necros can dispense. Thank you for your time.</p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
