et to a respectable int level very quickly.<br>As far as night vision goes, iksar may not get infravision, but they get night vision, the harvester has effect: deadeye which has night vision and call of bones gives infravision too.  so vision is NOT a problem to any necro and if u choose a de for that reason you need help.  <br>There is really no reason to make a de necro as far as i can see. If you want to go the route of getting as large a mana pool as possible, make an erudite.  If u want to level quickly (well faster than other necros) be an iksar.  If u want to be original be a gnome or a human(course there are not a TON of iksar necros yet).  If u want to be the most played out, obvious and really have nothin going for you other than blue skin and infravision, be a Dark Elf..... well ive vented now =) ty.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sun Jan 13 03:34:41 2002</em></p>&nbsp;<br>Fendrish 52 Barb War<br>Deadinc 46 Iksar Necro<br></td></td></tr>
